very flexible in the centre. The typical plans are b4-b5 or e4-d4 at an
appropriate moment.} N8d7 11. b3 (11. e4 {is premature due to} Nc5 12. Rd1 Ne6
{And Black controls the important d4-square.}) (11. Bg5) 11... Nd5 12. Bb2 Nxc3
13. Bxc3 Re8 14. b4 (14. Rfd1 h6 15. e4 Nc5 16. d4 (16. Nxe5) 16... exd4 17.
