(7... f6 {And now, most precise is} 8. a4 $1 a5 9. Nf4 Bf7 10. Bg2 c6 11. e4
$16 {, after which} e5 {fails to} 12. exd5 $3 exf4 13. dxc6 $18 {One critical
line here is} Bd6 14. cxb7 Rb8 15. Nb5 {, and due to the inclusion of 8.a4 a5,
the knight is protected after 15...Qe7+ 16.Kf1 Bc4+}) 8. Nf4 Bg6 9. Bg2 ({
