Rd7 Rh4 35. Rxd5 Rxd5 36. Bxd5 Rxa4 37. Bxb7 Rb4 38. Bd5 a4 39. Nd2 Kc5 40. Bf7
Rxb2 41. Ne4+ Kd4 42. Nd6 a3 43. Kg2 a2 44. Bxa2 Rxa2 45. Kg3 Kd5 46. Nf7 Ke6
47. Ng5+ Kf5 48. Nf3 g5 49. Nd4+ Kg6 50. Nf3 Ra4 51. Ne5+ Kf5 52. Nd3 Ra3 {
0-1 Gaal,Z-Maurizzi,M/chess24.com INT 2022}) 9... Bh5 (9... Bc8 10. e4 $36) 10.
g4 Bg6 11. g5 Ng8 12. e4 e6 13. f4 $3 dxe4 14. f5 exf5 15. Nxf5 $36 Ne7 16. Ng3
) 6. Nh4 Bg4 (6... Be4 $2 7. Nxe4 dxe4 (7... Nxe4 8. c4 $3 e6 9. c5 Nd7 10. Qc2
Nef6 (10... f5 11. f3 Nef6 12. e4 $18) 11. b4 $16) 8. c3 e6 9. Qc2 $16 Qd5 10.
f3 exf3 11. Bxf3) (6... e6 {transposes to 4...Bf5:} 7. Nxf5 exf5 8. Qd3 g6 9.
Bg5 Be7 10. Bxf6 Bxf6 11. e3 O-O 12. O-O c6 13. b3 $14) 7. h3 Bh5 8. g4 ({
Also good is} 8. Qd3 $5 e6 9. O-O Be7 10. g4 Bg6 11. Nxg6 hxg6 12. e4 dxe4 13.
Nxe4 Nxe4 14. Qxe4 c6 15. b3 O-O 16. c4 Bf6 17. Be3 $14) 8... Bg6 9. Nxg6 hxg6
10. g5 (10. e4 $5 {is also possible.}) 10... Ng8 (10... Nh5 {may be the lesser
evil, sidelining the knight but forcing White to keep am eye on the f4-square.}
) 11. e4 dxe4 12. Nxe4 $16 *

