premature. White should play in the centre to punish Black for his neglected
development.} 5. c4 {Black will not be able to justify the move h7-h5 in the
following Reti- or Catalan-type position. There is no kingside attack.} ({
Equally good is} 5. d4 {, followed by c2-c4.}) *

